---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Products | Wyre Digital"
  description="Discover WYRE stablecoin and Immutable Records on BSV blockchain."
>
  <div class="page-wrapper line-bg">
    <div class="section_hero">
      <div class="padding-global-2">
        <div class="container-large">
          <div class="features_content-wrapper">
            <h1><strong>Two Products. One Mission.</strong></h1>
            <p>Building robust financial infrastructure on BSV for the future.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section_body-content">
      <div class="padding-global-2">
        <div class="container-large">
          <div class="padding-section-medium">
            <h2>WYRE</h2>
            <div class="spacer-medium"></div>
            <div class="div_fake-button-wrapper">
              <p class="fake-button"><strong>1:1 Fiat Backed</strong></p>
              <p class="fake-button"><strong>&lt;$0.01/tx</strong></p>
              <p class="fake-button"><strong>1M+ TPS</strong></p>
            </div>
            <div class="spacer-medium"></div>
            <h3>How It Works</h3>
            <ul role="list">
              <li class="underlined"><strong>Mint:</strong> Deposit fiat and receive WYRE tokens.</li>
              <li class="underlined"><strong>Transact:</strong> Send and receive with minimal fees.</li>
              <li class="underlined"><strong>Redeem:</strong> Exchange WYRE for fiat anytime.</li>
              <li class="underlined"><strong>Verify:</strong> Check transactions on the blockchain.</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="spacer-medium"></div>
            <h3>Why BSV</h3>
            <ul role="list">
              <li class="underlined">Unlimited scalability</li>
              <li class="underlined">Ultra-low transaction costs</li>
              <li class="underlined">High throughput for enterprise use</li>
              <li class="underlined">Proven security</li>
              <li class="underlined">Open and permissionless</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="spacer-medium"></div>
            <h3>Use Cases</h3>
            <ul role="list">
              <li class="underlined">Cross-border remittances</li>
              <li class="underlined">Micropayments</li>
              <li class="underlined">DeFi applications</li>
              <li class="underlined">Supply chain finance</li>
              <li class="underlined">Gaming economies</li>
              <li class="underlined">Enterprise treasury management</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="spacer-medium"></div>
            <h3>Join the Waitlist</h3>
            <form action="/contact" method="post">
              <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Enter your email" required>
              <button type="submit">Sign Up</button>
            </form>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section_body-content">
      <div class="padding-global-2">
        <div class="container-large">
          <div class="padding-section-medium">
            <h2>Immutable Records</h2>
            <p>Tamper-proof data anchoring for compliance and auditing.</p>
            <a href="/immutable-records" class="button is-large w-button">Learn More</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>